<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<definitions xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:camunda="http://camunda.org/schema/1.0/bpmn" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:zeebe="http://camunda.org/schema/zeebe/1.0" exporter="Camunda Modeler" exporterVersion="4.12.0" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.signavio.com/bpmn20" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL BPMN20.xsd">
    
  <process id="TwitterDemoProcess" isClosed="false" isExecutable="true" name="TwitterDemoProcess" processType="None">
        
    <startEvent id="start_event_new_tweet" isInterrupting="true" name="New Tweet
written" parallelMultiple="false">
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_new_tweet</outgoing>
          
    </startEvent>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_new_tweet" sourceRef="start_event_new_tweet" targetRef="user_task_review_tweet"/>
        
    <exclusiveGateway gatewayDirection="Unspecified" id="gateway_approved" name="Tweet approved?">
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_tweet_reviewed</incoming>
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_approved_no</outgoing>
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_approved_yes</outgoing>
          
    </exclusiveGateway>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_approved_no" name="No" sourceRef="gateway_approved" targetRef="service_task_send_rejection_notification">
            
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">=approved=false</conditionExpression>
          
    </sequenceFlow>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_approved_yes" name="Yes" sourceRef="gateway_approved" targetRef="service_task_publish_on_twitter">
            
      <conditionExpression id="condition_approved_yes" xsi:type="tFormalExpression">=approved</conditionExpression>
          
    </sequenceFlow>
        
    <userTask camunda:assignee="demo" camunda:candidateUsers="demo" completionQuantity="1" id="user_task_review_tweet" implementation="##unspecified" isForCompensation="false" name="Review tweet" startQuantity="1">
            
      <extensionElements>
                
        <zeebe:assignmentDefinition assignee="=boss"/>
              
      </extensionElements>
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_duplicate_handled</incoming>
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_new_tweet</incoming>
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_tweet_reviewed</outgoing>
          
    </userTask>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_tweet_reviewed" name="" sourceRef="user_task_review_tweet" targetRef="gateway_approved"/>
        
    <serviceTask camunda:class="twitter.RejectionNotificationDelegate" completionQuantity="1" id="service_task_send_rejection_notification" implementation="##WebService" isForCompensation="false" name="Send rejection notification" startQuantity="1">
            
      <extensionElements>
                
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="send-rejection"/>
              
      </extensionElements>
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_approved_no</incoming>
            
      <outgoing>sequqnce_flow_rejection_sent</outgoing>
          
    </serviceTask>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequqnce_flow_rejection_sent" sourceRef="service_task_send_rejection_notification" targetRef="end_event_tweet_rejected"/>
        
    <endEvent id="end_event_tweet_rejected" name="Tweet rejected">
            
      <incoming>sequqnce_flow_rejection_sent</incoming>
          
    </endEvent>
        
    <boundaryEvent attachedToRef="service_task_publish_on_twitter" cancelActivity="true" id="boundary_event_tweet_duplicated" name="Tweet duplicated" parallelMultiple="false">
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_tweet_duplicated</outgoing>
            
      <errorEventDefinition errorRef="error_tweet_duplicated" id="error_event_definition_tweet_duplicated"/>
          
    </boundaryEvent>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_tweet_duplicated" name="" sourceRef="boundary_event_tweet_duplicated" targetRef="user_task_handle_duplicate"/>
        
    <serviceTask camunda:delegateExpression="#{tweetPublicationDelegate}" completionQuantity="1" id="service_task_publish_on_twitter" implementation="##WebService" isForCompensation="false" name="Publish on Twitter" startQuantity="1">
            
      <extensionElements>
                
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="publish-tweet"/>
              
      </extensionElements>
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_approved_yes</incoming>
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_tweet_published</outgoing>
          
    </serviceTask>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_tweet_published" sourceRef="service_task_publish_on_twitter" targetRef="end_event_tweet_published"/>
        
    <endEvent id="end_event_tweet_published" name="Tweet published">
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_tweet_published</incoming>
          
    </endEvent>
        
    <userTask completionQuantity="1" id="user_task_handle_duplicate" implementation="##unspecified" isForCompensation="false" name="Handle duplicate tweet" startQuantity="1">
            
      <extensionElements>
                
        <zeebe:assignmentDefinition assignee="=author"/>
              
      </extensionElements>
            
      <incoming>sequence_flow_tweet_duplicated</incoming>
            
      <outgoing>sequence_flow_duplicate_handled</outgoing>
          
    </userTask>
        
    <sequenceFlow id="sequence_flow_duplicate_handled" name="" sourceRef="user_task_handle_duplicate" targetRef="user_task_review_tweet"/>
      
  </process>
    
  <error errorCode="duplicateMessage" id="error_tweet_duplicated" name="Tweet duplicated"/>
